title: Cornish Arms
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hotel bar with a comfy lounge area. Offers pub food and has a separate vegan menu that includes pizza, faux chicken parmigiana, burger, falafel, and chips. Specials include vegan burgers, vegan fish and chips and vegan BBQ. Hosts trivia on some nights - see website for details.
